task.description:
Create run_factorial_evaluation() that systematically evaluates all
combinations in the factorial design. Iterates over:

for checkpoint in 216_checkpoints:
  for fold_strategy in [single_best, cv_average]:
    for recalibration in [none, temperature_scaling]:
      for ensemble in [none, within_family, cross_family, all_trainable, all_zeroshot]:
        evaluate_and_log(...)

Each evaluation point logs per-volume metrics to MLflow with tags:
- model, loss, aux_calib, post_training_method
- fold_strategy, recalibration, ensemble_strategy
- experiment_name="factorial_evaluation_v1"

Skips invalid combinations (e.g., within_family ensemble needs >=2 losses).
